<font color="yellow">Burungnya cantik sekali.</font>

4
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:16,730
<font color="yellow">Ada ibu burung, bayi burung, ayah burung...</font>

5
00:00:16,730 --> 00:00:18,960
<font color="yellow">...dan teman-temannya.
Mereka semuanya sedang terbang.</font>

6
00:00:29,890 --> 00:00:31,130
<font color="yellow">Ibu, ulurkan tanganmu.</font>

7
00:00:35,190 --> 00:00:37,590
<font color="yellow">Pegang ini. Pegang.</font>

8
00:00:45,190 --> 00:00:46,230
<font color="yellow">Pegang yang erat.</font>

9
00:01:04,430 --> 00:01:05,430
<font color="yellow">Jeong A.</font>

10
00:01:24,090 --> 00:01:25,090
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

11
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,930
<font color="yellow">Lihatlah burungnya.</font>

12
00:02:22,830 --> 00:02:24,160
<font color="yellow">Cukup.</font>

13
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:25,730
<font color="yellow">Awas sampai aku menangkapmu.</font>

14
00:02:25,730 --> 00:02:28,460
<font color="yellow">Kau belum menang./
Lihat.</font>

15
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,770
<font color="yellow">Lihat sana.</font>

16
00:02:29,770 --> 00:02:31,840
<font color="yellow">Tidak./
Sudah.</font>

17
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,690
<font color="yellow">Unni menangis.</font>

18
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,630
<font color="yellow">Ada apa?</font>

19
00:02:56,490 --> 00:02:58,190
<font color="yellow">Ibu sudah tiada.</font>

20
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:04,390
<font color="yellow">Ibunya Jeong A meninggal.</font>

21
00:03:05,530 --> 00:03:09,200
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia janda selama 50 tahun yang lalu,
bertani sepanjang hidupnya...</i></font>

22
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,830
<font color="yellow"><i>...demi membesarkan ketiga anaknya.</i></font>

23
00:03:11,490 --> 00:03:15,490
<font color="yellow"><i>Dia menghabiskan tujuh tahun di panti
jompo karena banyak penyakit dideritanya...,</i></font>

24
00:03:16,330 --> 00:03:20,330
<font color="yellow"><i>...dan pada perjalanan pertamanya ke
pantai bersama putrinya tercinta...,</i></font>

25
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,390
<font color="yellow"><i>...ibunya meninggal.</i></font>

26
00:03:23,330 --> 00:03:24,360
<font color="yellow">Nenek?</font>

27
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:26,390
<font color="yellow">Bukannya kau harus kesana?</font>

28
00:03:27,330 --> 00:03:28,490
<font color="yellow">Biarkan saja dulu.</font>

29
00:03:29,390 --> 00:03:31,260
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana ini?</font>

30
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:35,160
<font color="yellow">Apa lagi? Kita harus
urus jadwal pemakaman.</font>

31
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:40,060
<font color="yellow">Unni.</font>

32
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,860
<font color="yellow">Ibunya Jeong A baru saja meninggal.</font>

33
00:03:43,990 --> 00:03:46,530
<font color="yellow">Sekarang juga? Di pantai.</font>

34
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:51,860
<font color="yellow">Aku menelepon Unni karena
kau sering mengurusi pemakaman.</font>

35
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:55,060
<font color="yellow">Aku nanti telepon Seok Gyun Oppa.</font>

36
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,030
<font color="yellow">Oh, benarkah?</font>

37
00:03:58,030 --> 00:04:00,390
<font color="yellow">Kita harus panggil ambulans?</font>

38
00:04:01,130 --> 00:04:04,030
<font color="yellow">Mereka mengirim ambulan kalau
ada orang meninggal?</font>

39
00:04:04,930 --> 00:04:08,790
<font color="yellow"><i>Ada saat-saat ketika aku merasa tidak berguna bagaikan kerang di pantai...</i></font>

40
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:12,080
<font color="yellow"><i>...karena kurangnya pengalaman
karena orang dewasa...</i></font>

41
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,060
<font color="yellow"><i>...tampak begitu kuat dan tahu semuanya.</i></font>

42
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:19,230
<font color="yellow">Bibi Yeong Won?</font>

43
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:25,990
<font color="yellow">Ibunya Bibi Jeong A barusan meninggal.</font>

44
00:04:27,190 --> 00:04:28,400
<font color="yellow">Bagaimana ini?</font>

45
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:56,630
<font color="yellow">Oh, begitu. Baiklah.</font>

46
00:04:57,030 --> 00:05:00,030
<font color="yellow">Kalau sudah diputuskan
tempat penguburannya...,</font>

47
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,360
<font color="yellow">...telepon aku ya.</font>

48
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:10,030
<font color="yellow">Aku tak percaya aku merias wajahku
cari uang...</font>

49
00:05:10,030 --> 00:05:11,930
<font color="yellow">...padahal barusan ada orang meninggal.</font>

50
00:05:13,960 --> 00:05:16,230
<font color="yellow">Mereka sudah siap sekarang.</font>

51
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:19,430
<font color="yellow">Oke, aku datang. Ayo pergi.</font>

52
00:05:19,430 --> 00:05:21,330
<font color="yellow">Begitulah yang orang pikirkan.</font>

53
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,890
<font color="yellow">Beraninya kau?/
Apa?</font>

54
00:05:24,890 --> 00:05:26,250
<font color="yellow">Hei!/
Beraninya kau?</font>

55
00:05:26,250 --> 00:05:28,220
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan rambutku!</font>

56
00:05:28,220 --> 00:05:30,420
<font color="yellow">Lepaskan aku! Sekarang juga!</font>

57
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:32,040
<font color="yellow"><i>Ketika mereka menentukan
garis kehidupan...</i></font>

58
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:35,260
<font color="yellow"><i>Ketika mereka mengatakan orang mati ya harus mati dan orang yang hidup harus melanjutkan hidup mereka.</i></font>

59
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:40,760
<font color="yellow"><i>Ketika mereka memisahkan apa yang bisa dilakukan dan yang tidak bisa dilakukan.</i></font>

60
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,300
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak mengerti?</font>

61
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:46,450
<font color="yellow">Kami belum memutuskan tempatnya.</font>

62
00:05:46,450 --> 00:05:47,930
<font color="yellow">Aku akan meneleponmu kalau...</font>

63
00:05:49,190 --> 00:05:51,790
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu dmana?
Biar aku bicara dengan anakmu.</font>

64
00:05:52,490 --> 00:05:54,570
<font color="yellow">Dia jatuh di kamar mandi?</font>

65
00:05:54,570 --> 00:05:58,130
<font color="yellow">Kalau begitu jangan datang ke pemakaman atau kami juga harus menguburmu.</font>

66
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:02,380
<font color="yellow"><i>Ketika mereka bilang itu bagian dari kehidupan.</i>/ Angkatlah.</font>

67
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:05,080
<font color="yellow"><i>Saat itulah kupikir para orang tua
kelihatan hebat...,</i></font>

68
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:06,860
<font color="yellow"><i>...mengesankan dan tak terkalahkan.</i></font>

69
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,810
<font color="yellow">Dia sudah gila?</font>

70
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:11,620
<font color="yellow">Jeong A Unni dan Seok Gyun Oppa
tinggal selama tiga hari saat ibunya...</font>

71
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:14,300
<font color="yellow">...dan ayahnya meninggal dan dia
tidak mau datang?</font>

72
00:06:14,300 --> 00:06:16,480
<font color="yellow">Kenapa tidak? Dia bakalan lelah?</font>

73
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:19,940
<font color="yellow">Putrinya akhirnya menetapkan
tanggal pernikahannya...</font>

74
00:06:19,940 --> 00:06:21,860
<font color="yellow">...dan bilang bakalan sial kalau
datang ke pemakaman.</font>

75
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:23,230
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu.</font>

76
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,430
<font color="yellow">Itulah maksudku.</font>

77
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:28,930
<font color="yellow">Sejak kapan dia mulai nurut sama istrinya?</font>

78
00:06:29,330 --> 00:06:33,690
<font color="yellow">Terus dia juga harus izin
kalau mau selingkuh?</font>

79
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,400
<font color="yellow">Bodoh.</font>

80
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,690
<font color="yellow">Kalau dia meninggal, kita tidak
usah ke pemakamannya.</font>

81
00:06:40,260 --> 00:06:41,260
<font color="yellow">Oh, iya.</font>

82
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:43,830
<font color="yellow">Kalau kasih sumbangan
30 dolar diterima tidak?</font>

83
00:06:44,190 --> 00:06:47,560
<font color="yellow">Oh, terus kalau pesan makanan...,</font>

84
00:06:48,190 --> 00:06:50,560
<font color="yellow">...pesan makanan fermentasi ya.</font>

85
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,490
<font color="yellow">Itu mahal.</font>

86
00:06:52,890 --> 00:06:54,600
<font color="yellow">Cumi-cumi saja ya.</font>

87
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:58,210
<font color="yellow">Saudaranya Jeong A petani.
Mereka tidak mampu.</font>

88
00:06:58,210 --> 00:07:00,580
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau mau makan itu?</font>

89
00:07:00,580 --> 00:07:03,900
<font color="yellow">Kita harus makan itu! Biasanya acara pemakaman ada menu makanan itu!</font>

90
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:05,930
<font color="yellow">Apa kau juga akan berhemat di pemakamanku?</font>

91
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:11,260
<font color="yellow">Oke, baiklah.</font>

92
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,690
<font color="yellow">Di mana rumah dukanya?</font>

93
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:15,810
<font color="yellow">Kenapa lagi ini pesan makanan?</font>

94
00:07:15,810 --> 00:07:17,780
<font color="yellow">Bukankah rumah duka yang
mengatur semuanya?</font>

95
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:19,720
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kita belanja...</font>

96
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:20,830
<font color="yellow">Diam.</font>

97
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:23,360
<font color="yellow">Astaga.</font>

98
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,690
<font color="yellow">Kita sudah beli semua ini.</font>

99
00:07:29,790 --> 00:07:33,160
<font color="yellow">Noona, Ibu menentangku
meminang gadis Filipina.</font>

100
00:07:33,490 --> 00:07:35,430
<font color="yellow">Kau?</font>

101
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:37,650
<font color="yellow">Dia itu baru 20 tahun.</font>

102
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:38,690
<font color="yellow">22.</font>

103
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,390
<font color="yellow">Kau mau apa dengan.../
Pembohong.</font>

104
00:07:41,930 --> 00:07:43,330
<font color="yellow">Bilang saja ini karena kakiku.</font>

105
00:07:48,030 --> 00:07:49,590
<font color="yellow">Ibu. Ibu.</font>

106
00:07:50,860 --> 00:07:51,860
<font color="yellow">Hei.</font>

107
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,090
<font color="yellow">Tunggu disini. Ibu!</font>

108
00:07:58,860 --> 00:07:59,860
<font color="yellow">Ibu.</font>

109
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:02,690
<font color="yellow">Buat apa baju ini?</font>

110
00:08:03,690 --> 00:08:07,190
<font color="yellow">Benar. Aku bisa saja mati besok.
Aku tidak perlu baju baru.</font>

111
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:18,030
<font color="yellow">Terus kenapa kalau aku mati besok?
Aku bisa beli apa yang kumau.</font>

112
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:19,790
<font color="yellow">Belikan itu untukku.</font>

113
00:08:31,330 --> 00:08:32,450
<font color="yellow">Halo?</font>

114
00:08:32,450 --> 00:08:33,970
<font color="yellow">Hei, Nak.</font>

115
00:08:33,970 --> 00:08:35,260
<font color="yellow">Kenapa lama sekali angkat teleponnya?</font>

116
00:08:36,430 --> 00:08:38,950
<font color="yellow">Oh, halo, Chang Soo.</font>

117
00:08:38,950 --> 00:08:40,680
<font color="yellow">Mau bertemu saja kita
harus ke pemakaman.</font>

118
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:42,380
<font color="yellow">Kudengar dia meninggal di tempat terbuka.</font>

119
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:44,780
<font color="yellow">Iya. Masuklah ke dalam.</font>

120
00:08:44,780 --> 00:08:46,090
<font color="yellow">Baik.</font>

121
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:50,230
<font color="yellow">Hei, Nak. Kapan kau sampai di sini?</font>

122
00:08:53,660 --> 00:08:54,690
<font color="yellow">Siapa ini?</font>

123
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:02,630
<font color="yellow">Apa Ibu juga punya Ibu?</font>

124
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:05,830
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja. Nenekmu.</font>

125
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:08,890
<font color="yellow">Kau tidak pernah melihatnya
karena dia mati muda.</font>

126
00:09:09,430 --> 00:09:10,460
<font color="yellow">Aneh...</font>

127
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,760
<font color="yellow">...ibuku juga punya ibu.</font>

128
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:16,530
<font color="yellow">Ya, aku punya ibu.</font>

129
00:09:21,460 --> 00:09:23,260
<font color="yellow">Limusin?</font>

130
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,650
<font color="yellow">Tidak./
Tidak.</font>

131
00:09:27,650 --> 00:09:29,920
<font color="yellow">Peti mati. Royal foxglove, juniper...,</font>

132
00:09:29,920 --> 00:09:31,880
<font color="yellow">...kayu pohon pinus atau
lauan, yang termurah.</font>

133
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:34,050
<font color="yellow">Kita tidak bisa pilih lauan.
Harus royal foxglove.</font>

134
00:09:34,050 --> 00:09:36,520
<font color="yellow">Lauan saja. Lagipula kau tak pernah
peduli waktu dia masih hidup.</font>

135
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:38,500
<font color="yellow">Tidak bisa.../
Lauan saja.</font>

136
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:42,110
<font color="yellow">Berapa harganya?
Aku sudah tua, tapi aku mengerti semua ini.</font>

137
00:09:42,110 --> 00:09:43,890
<font color="yellow">Pastikan kau hitung dengan benar.</font>

138
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:48,890
<font color="yellow">Ibu! Ibu...</font>

139
00:09:49,530 --> 00:09:50,730
<font color="yellow">Ibu!</font>

140
00:09:51,460 --> 00:09:54,180
<font color="yellow">Kenapa dia?</font>

141
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,960
<font color="yellow">Jangan sekarang.</font>

142
00:09:56,890 --> 00:09:58,850
<font color="yellow">Noona.../
Ikut aku.</font>

143
00:09:58,850 --> 00:10:00,930
<font color="yellow">Hidupkan dia./
Kemari.</font>

144
00:10:01,660 --> 00:10:03,190
<font color="yellow">Ayo keluar.</font>

145
00:10:04,430 --> 00:10:07,500
<font color="yellow">Ayo./
Ibuku yang malang...</font>

146
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:13,330
<font color="yellow">Sudahlah. Ayo keluar.</font>

147
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:16,160
<font color="yellow">Wanita yang malang...</font>

148
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:21,990
<font color="yellow"><i>Rangkaian acara pemakaman
ibunya Bibi Jeong...</i></font>

149
00:10:21,990 --> 00:10:24,330
<font color="yellow"><i>...selesai dalam empat hari.</i></font>

150
00:10:41,060 --> 00:10:43,460
<font color="yellow">Apa saudaramu membolehkanmu
mengambil abunya?</font>

151
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:46,260
<font color="yellow">Mereka marah pada Unni
karena kau tidak baik sama ibumu.</font>

152
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:50,030
<font color="yellow">Mereka mengira ibu mereka dirawat
di tempat yang bagus.</font>

153
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,410
<font color="yellow">Unni sudah banyak membantu.</font>

154
00:10:52,410 --> 00:10:54,800
<font color="yellow">Ibuku sudah mengalami
kehidupan yang bising.</font>

155
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:56,460
<font color="yellow">Jadi dia benci keributan.</font>

156
00:10:57,090 --> 00:10:58,090
<font color="yellow">Biarkan dia istirahat dalam damai.</font>

157
00:10:59,630 --> 00:11:02,130
<font color="yellow">Tugas kita melakukan hal ini.</font>

158
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:23,620
<font color="yellow"><i>Ibunya Bibi Jeong A, yang
memiliki kehidupan yang berat...,</i></font>

159
00:11:23,620 --> 00:11:25,060
<font color="yellow"><i>...ditaburkan dalam angin...</i></font>

160
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,330
<font color="yellow"><i>...dan dalam ombak.</i></font>

161
00:11:28,590 --> 00:11:32,360
<font color="yellow"><i>Suatu hari, mereka semua akan tiada.</i></font>

162
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:33,790
<font color="yellow"><i>Dan juga pada...</i></font>

163
00:11:35,660 --> 00:11:36,690
<font color="yellow"><i>...ibuku.</i></font>

164
00:11:41,530 --> 00:11:43,260
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, jalani saja.</font>

165
00:11:46,660 --> 00:11:48,860
<font color="yellow">Ini keinginan Ibu.
Aku akan menulis tentang mereka.</font>

166
00:11:49,730 --> 00:11:50,730
<font color="yellow">Cerita ibuku...</font>

167
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:52,390
<font color="yellow">...dan cerita bibi-bibi...</font>

168
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:58,760
<font color="yellow">Daripada menyesal di kemudian hari,
aku lebih baik menulis tentang mereka.</font>

169
00:12:13,990 --> 00:12:16,010
<font color="yellow">Dia memanggilmu "Nak?"</font>

170
00:12:16,010 --> 00:12:19,500
<font color="yellow">Iya. Dia melakukan itu sepanjang waktu.</font>

171
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,560
<font color="yellow">Aku takut ada orang
yang dengar.</font>

172
00:12:29,760 --> 00:12:31,660
<font color="yellow"><i>Selamat malam, Nak.</i></font>

173
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:33,960
<font color="yellow">Kenapa dia ini?</font>

174
00:12:40,730 --> 00:12:42,890
<font color="yellow"><i>[Choong Nam]</i></font>

175
00:12:44,830 --> 00:12:46,490
<font color="yellow">Aku mau dengar rekamannya.</font>

176
00:12:51,030 --> 00:12:52,210
<font color="yellow"><i>Iya.</i></font>

177
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,690
<font color="yellow"><i>Ya, aku memukulnya.</i></font>

178
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:55,830
<font color="yellow"><i>Malah, setiap kali. Terus kenapa?</i></font>

179
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:58,580
<font color="yellow">Bisakah kita menghancurkannya dengan rekaman itu?/ <i>Kau punya bukti?</i></font>

180
00:12:58,580 --> 00:13:00,930
<font color="yellow"><i>Tidak? Dia menyakiti dirinya sendiri!</i></font>

181
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:05,390
<font color="yellow">Oppa berhati dingin.</font>

182
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:11,890
<font color="yellow">Unni? Dae Cheol...</font>

183
00:13:12,730 --> 00:13:13,860
<font color="yellow">...mengirimku bunga.</font>

184
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:17,560
<font color="yellow">Bukannya dia sudah menikah?</font>

185
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:20,830
<font color="yellow">Tentu saja sudah.</font>

